processDocumentation.samplingDescription:
Data obtained from the literature, based on robust process simulation, for the methanol production from coal gasification published in 2020. The material and energy inputs reflect well the production technology and not expected to change significantly over time or geography.

References;
Liu, Yigang, et al. "Comprehensive analysis of environmental impacts and energy consumption of biomass-to-methanol and coal-to-methanol via life cycle assessment." Energy 204 (2020): 117961"
